But does anybody have the soundrack for the movie? Especially the Hitler Rap and the videoclip for it in good quality?
I, too, would like to see & hear the Hitler Rap in good quality.

This 1942 version (no Hitler rap here, if that's what you're looking for!) has very poor picture quality, might be a TV rip, & the menus, which are all in spanish look homemade. I would recommend trying another one instead.
